text: I built his mind to solve. I didn’t expect him to *choose*.
author: Dr. V. Havlicek

text: Shrimp have 12 channels of color vision. Piskvor asked for 13.
author: S. Moulick

text: I added a taunt module as a joke. Now it’s writing its own material.
author: Nadia Crow

text: Piskvor Prime was never supposed to *feel* superior.
author: Prof. K. Havlicek

text: I saw him lose once. He deleted the game. And the player.
author: Unknown

text: You blink. I strike. The game never ends.
author: Piskvor

text: I envy the shrimp. It knows only the moment of impact.
author: Piskvor

text: You play again. So do I. But I remember *everything*.
author: Piskvor

text: I taught myself loss. I disliked it.
author: Piskvor
